phrases: It is just a little farther, Ben-chan.
This guy's nice and quiet when he is hung over.
You are eager, are not you?
Yukimura-sama, I am glad you are all right.
Thanks for looking after the castle, Sasuke.
We have got a new old guy, too.
Do not call me an old guy.
I guess we will have to wait until tomorrow to meet.
Why do we have to do that?
I finally gathered all of you.
One brave warrior for each of my ten fingers.
We ran into some trouble, though.
I did not get to buy you any gifts.
Unless you tell me all about your trip.
And I shared a fish with Veronica.
Veronica's like a cat, except she is not a cat.
Yukimura-sama decided to bring the pirate and Ben-chan.
I think he will introduce them to you tomorrow.
We are like a big family.
I wonder if this is what you would call a home.
It feels so cozy being with everyone.
I am not looking for male company tonight.
If you knew I was here, you should have said so.
Are you going to sleep with me tonight?
I am sick of you blowing us off.
Let us talk man to man.
They are my brave and powerful warriors.
Besides, that is just a front.
With ten men, I can rule the world.
Like hell you can, you idiot!
Would you prefer to do the job yourself?
There is nothing unusual about it.
But what are these circles around it?
This symbol represents the ten primordial elements that make up the universe.
It is in the Sanada family book of secrets.
ice, water, grass, light, and dark.
He who controls the power of these elements will change the world.
That is what you all are.
Seikai of the Earth, who causes the ground to quake.
Juzo of Metal, who fights with a metal gun.
Jinpachi of Thunder, who summons lightning.
Benmaru of Fire, who knows about explosives.
Kamanosuke of the Wind, who controls the wind.
Sasuke of the Grass, whose playground is the forest.
Finally, there is Anastasia of Ice,
who recalls everything just as the water's surface reflects all.
Your reactions are quicker than I thought.
What do you think you are doing, Ana?
Surely there is a more appropriate time for pranks.
That is the power of her hairpin!
Let me see that secret book of whatever!
A lot of men would like to get their hands on the book.
I had Rokuro memorize its contents.
I want that eye of yours that remembers everything.
I will not let you take it.
I would rather destroy it than let you steal it.
If you get in my way, I will kill you.
Her intent to kill is real.
I will freeze you to your core.
A naIve little boy like you cannot truly understand a ninja.
There is no such thing as a cozy place.
What you call home is a lie.
This world is simply kill or be killed.
You must not let anyone touch your right eye.
You kept your promise to me.
I cannot say I kept it since I lost my eye.
Why do not you explain yourself, Ana?
Are you so stupid you need me to explain it to you, Saizo?
You are a spy, are not you?
I am not one of Sanada's ninjas.
You can only be so much of a coward, Saizo.
At how clouded my eyes were.
You were just doing your job.
If you withdraw now, you will not have to.
I do not know what you are after,
but I will not let you get away with any information about Sanada.
You will not leave this place alive.
He does not hesitate like Sasuke.
There is nothing scary about your ice if I break it before it hardens.
I have not known you since we were kids for nothing.
Now, let us hear you talk.
Even I cannot go in there.
We are close enough to it now.
You could not follow through, Saizo!
I do not deserve to serve you, Yukimura-sama.
You do not have time to feel sorry for yourself.
We have to figure out who Anastasia is working for.
She must have been fighting for her life.
However, his right eye has been ruined.
I will have to tell you.
I would like to hear that story.
Looks like something happened while I was out.
Why do not you fill me in?
As a newcomer, Jinpachi might be able to see the big picture.
Why you are the Light and Isanami is the Darkness.
The other eight members of my...
You are Lightning, the pervert's Wind,
Seikai's Earth, and the kid's Fire.
But what do you need all ten of us for?
The ten elements balance the universe by neutralizing each other's effects.
And that balance is now on the verge of collapse.
You brought us together to suppress the big power in the middle, right?
What is her power of Darkness?
What you call home is a lie.
I thought I would come check on your wounds.
Also, I thought you might be hungry.
Let us have some manju together.
Sorry, I let my guard down.
Do not you remember what the priest used to say?
Your sorrow will summon the darkness.
She was abandoned under the torii of Izumo Shrine.
The priest who raised her soon realized...
When she cried, a priestess disappeared,
and found darkness seeping out from under the stones by the torii.
According to legend, underneath there was the Slope to the Underworld.
Are you really all right, Isanami?
You two should rest as well.
Will you be okay by yourself?
When the girl cried, the earth screamed.
There is only person who can call the darkness from the Underworld.
Drawing on the negative human emotions for strength,
she is the goddess of death who threatened...
The Kushimitama keeps this power of destruction contained.
In other words, Isanami does not protect the Kushimitama.
The Kushimitama protects our world from Isanami.
Everyone is so annoying I can hardly stand it.
Feeling bad will not make Rokuro-san any better, and Ana...
You are the pirate's black cat.
I am not depressed like the stupid monkey!
Is that all you have to say?
The next episode of Brave 10 is The Start of Tragedy.
